data.description: Gravel Bikers, First Time Home Buyers, Investors: Seller to pay up to $7,000 for rate buy down. Charming 2-bed, 1-bath home w/recent upgrades - new luxury vinyl plank floors, interior paint, windows, HVAC, & granite counters. Potential for a 3rd bedroom w/ a closet in the spacious mudroom. Refrigerator conveys. Detached garage w/workshop, outside cellar for storage, & .46-acre lot w/chicken coop. Chickens, washer/dryer & outside playset negotiable. RD loan eligible. Near Butler Creek Auctions & the most popular gravel biking routes in NWA. Seven minutes from Gravette & 3 mins to shopping. A portion of this sale goes to ST JUDE!
